Basically, a good deal for the price we got on priceline (80 USD/night), but I sure wouldn't pay full price for it.	Valet parking is a rip-off, you can drive the 1/2 block yourself for more than half the price.	We parked in the self parking at it cost us $42 for about 4 days, which isn't to bad.	At regular price this hotel is very good and if you get a room through priceline it is a steal!